headline: How Attractive Is Capital One After Recent Double-Digit Gains and Improving Market Sentiment?
summary: Wondering what your next move should be with Capital One Financial? You are definitely not alone. After all, the stock has put together an impressive performance, gaining 2.7% over the last week, nearly 10% in the past month, and an astonishing 56.5% over the last year. Stretch the timeline out even further and the growth story becomes even more dramatic, with the stock up over 130% in three years and a remarkable 235.1% for the past five years.
